<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>PSG Summer Internship Permission</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 40px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .header { text-align: center; font-weight: bold; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0; }
    td, th { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top; }
    .signature { margin-top: 60px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h3 class="header">PSG COLLEGE OF TECHNOLOGY, COIMBATORE 641 004</h3>
  <h4 class="header">Permission and Undertaking for Summer Internship / Short Duration Internship</h4>

  <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{formatDate currentDate}}</p>

  <p><strong>From:</strong><br>{{student_name}}<br>{{roll_number}}</p>

  <p><strong>To:</strong><br>The Principal<br>PSG College of Technology<br>Coimbatore – 641004</p>

  <p>Through: The Head of the Department, Department of <strong>{{department}}</strong></p>

  <p><strong>Sub:</strong> Undertaking while pursuing Internship/Project Work in Industry / Institutions.</p>

  <p>I wish to inform that I have been offered Summer internship/Short Duration internship in the organization, details of which are provided below.</p>

  <table>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>Name & Address of the Industry / Institution with contact details</strong><br>
          {{company_name}}<br>{{company_address}}<br>{{company_city}}, {{company_state}}
      </td>
      <td><strong>Internship Period</strong><br>
          From: {{formatDate start_date}}<br>
          To: {{formatDate end_date}}
      </td>
      <td><strong>Name of Mentor/Guide in Industry</strong><br>
          {{guide_name_industry}}<br>{{guide_contact}}
      </td>
      <td><strong>Attendance Needed</strong><br>{{attendance_days}} days</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p>My CGPA up to semester <strong>{{semester_completed}}</strong> is <strong>{{cgpa}}</strong></p>

  <p><strong>I hereby undertake the following:</strong></p>
  <ol>
    <li>I will be regular and sincere in carrying out my internship at the above organization and I will obey the Rules and Regulations of the organization.</li>
    <li>I will obtain the attendance certificate and submit the same at academic section within a week from the last date of my internship and also submit the copy of the report of the internship to the HoD.</li>
    <li>I will study on my own, the syllabi covered in the class during my internship.</li>
    <li>Further, after return from internship, I will also complete the assessment components (except CA Test 1 if total CA tests are three) and laboratory experiments missed during the internship period after regular class hours.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed the offer letter for internship.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed parent’s consent Letter.</li>
  </ol>

  <div class="signature">
    <p>(Signature of the Student)</p>
    <table style="width:100%; margin-top: 40px;">
      <tr>
        <td>Tutor</td>
        <td>Guide (Dept)</td>
        <td>Programme Co-ordinator</td>
        <td>HoD</td>
        <td>Dean (P&T)</td>
        <td>Dean-Academic</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <p><strong>PRINCIPAL</strong></p>

  <div class="note" style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.9em;">
    <strong>NOTE:</strong> Original Form shall be submitted to Placement Office and Photo copies to Academic Section and Head of the Department.
  </div>

</body>
</html>